#' fastMatrix: Fast Random Matrix Generation
#'
#' @section Brief Description:
#' The package provides an efficient approach to generating random samples 
#' from a multivariate normal distribution.
#'
#' @details
#' The package implements efficient algorithms for generating random 
#' samples from a multivariate normal distribution. It includes various 
#' decomposition techniques and optimization methods, and it leverages 
#' RcppArma for high-performance matrix computations.
#'
#' @section Algorithms:
#' - Fast Generation with Standard Cholesky decomposition (`rmvnorm_tianhai`)
#' - Fast Generation with RcppArma based methods (`rmvnorm_tianhai_cppArma`)
#' - Fast Generation with AR1-based Cholesky decomposition (`rmvnorm_tianhai_ar1`)
#' - Fast Generation with Exponential-based decomposition (`rmvnorm_tianhai_ex`)
#'
#' @section Use Case:
#' Ideal for statistical simulations, machine learning applications,
#' and other areas requiring efficient generation of multivariate 
#' normal samples.
#'
#' @section Additional Information:
#' For more details, see the individual function documentation 
#' and vignettes included in the package.
#' 
#' @author Tianhai
#' @seealso \code{\link{rmvnorm_tianhai_ar1}}, \code{\link{rmvnorm_tianhai_ex}}, 
#' \code{\link{rmvnorm_tianhai}}, \code{\link{rmvnorm_tianhai_cppArma}}
#' @keywords package
#' @docType package
#' @name fastMatrix-package
NULL